#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint4x.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint4x.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：给定 1 个 seed 标量和 1 个 offset 块，返回 4 个 int32 类型的随机块。\n"
"Triton 的 Philox 伪随机数生成器的最高效入口点。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Given 1 seed scalar and 1 offset block, returns 4 random blocks of type int32.  \n"
"The most efficient entry point of Triton's Philox pseudo-random number generator.  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint4x.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.randint4x(\n"
" seed,\n"
" offset,\n"
" n_rounds: constexpr = 10\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

